module:
development.folder="dvlp">
module, individual, product, relationship, structure, process plant
This part of ISO 10303 specifies an application module to record:
classes of composition relationship, and the decomposition of a class of product into component classes of product ;
classes of connection relationship, and connections between classes of product;
classes of product that are used to make a class of connection;
classes of containment relationship, and relationships between classes of product and classes of container.
class of decomposition relationship, and the decomposition of a class of product into component classes of product;
class of connection relationship, and connection between classes of product;
class of usage of a product in a connection, and usage of a class of product in a class of connection;
class of containment relationship, and containment of a class of product by a class of container.
the structure of an individual product; The structure of an individual product is within the scope of the Individual_product_structure application module.
the involvement of classes of product, classes of documents, classes of people and classes of organisation in a class of activity. The involvement of classes of product, classes of documents, classes of people and classes of organisation in a class of activity is within the scope of the Class_of_involvement_in_activity application module.
